Puppet module: nagios

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages nagios software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include nagios              # Install and run nagios with standard configurations.
include nagios::disable     # Disable nagios service.
include nagios::disableboot # Disable nagios service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include nagios::absent      # Remove nagios package.

DEPENDENCIES:
